{"tid":1860494,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[#1睇懶人包] 網購外科口罩集中討論125","createTime":"2020-02-03T16:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T07:36:42.000Z","uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9d69cac66c6862ed6ef4237ac78c52305ff073b6","tid":1860494,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:26:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>內容及資料僅供參考，投資涉及風險，口罩價格可升亦可跌，甚至變成亳無價值。旅客在決定是否購買有關口罩之前應先閱讀有關風險評估，以了解該建議發售之詳細資料，並應就本身的財務、其他狀況及需要，詳細考慮並決定購買有關口罩是否切合本身特定的需要，若有需要更應咨詢其他專業意見，方可作出有關購買決定。<br />\n忠告：親自買罩 咪俾錢炒狗</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家基本上得返日本Amazon有現貨賣，<br />\n所以唔好買太多，到時禁運就真係攬炒一鑊熟。<br />\n<br />\n問呢個得唔得嘅，最少睇曬前2/3個post嘅圖。<br />\n<br />\n做開團團長嘅，求下你，你開個tg,wts gp出嚟畀人join，夠數就關link。<br />\n<br />\n間間集運都爆，唔好再問邊間快啲邊間好用，根本就無人知。<br />\n<br />\n記得留意返集運公司對體積重收費同要求，隨時運費貴過口罩本身，重有拒收嘅風險存在。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>麻煩大家Amazon唔好再用殘體字 有得揀英文/日文</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2bbd61859d3381f9caad240d74e1cff745b0fd2e","tid":1860494,"uid":56206,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:26:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uL3owK6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuL3owK6.jpg&h=b72e9e6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g5L6uwM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg5L6uwM.jpg&h=657483df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nothingseriousfans/posts/2670475433071055\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnothingseriousfans%2Fposts%2F2670475433071055&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdCK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3W